      • getCronSpecFromInput

        public java.lang.String getCronSpecFromInput()
        The format for the cron specification should be as follows: startMinute startHour dayOfMonth Month daysOfWeek Year the dayOfMonth and Month features are not used by Whitehat so the effect of setting them is unknown as usual, a * means all This is an unpublished feature of the WH interface, it is not included in the API
        Returns:
        String - the cron specification for this scan specification
